                     <interp inst="t18451215-308-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>for stealing 60lbs. weight of coals, value 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. the goods of <persName id="t18451215-name-712" type="victimName">
